thread.title: Nina Molina
thread.title_full: Chinese Laundry reviewed by Nina Molina

author: Nina Molina
title: Nina Molina
text: Honestly my review entails my absolute love for the Kristin Cavallari booty line that is really the only thing that I ordered I have wore my shoes out to the Bone and now I need to order new ones thank you very much for keeping the toe less booties in stock please keep them around long-term thank you very much. I would also like to see more wedge options that don't create such a high heel maybe with a 3 inch heel so us girls can actually wear them shopping and not kill themselves lol thank you. Please consider glittered bottoms for the wedges. Meaning of the shoe not the bottom of the shoe LOL the wedge part.
